{"title":"脸谱种种续集","authors":["沙鸥","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":9,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸谱种种续集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥诗  方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯雪峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反党的罪证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是青铜铸成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切推脱都是徒然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他隐蔽自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用“单干户”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖了一道壕堑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙忙以“检查思想”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当飘浮的白色烟幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来封锁我们的视线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史却在发言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十多年前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他提刀向党宣战……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那像狼窟似的丁陈集团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有他坐的交椅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听他的指点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是“单干”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老老实实吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要躲在壕堑里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装着轻轻拍灰尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这最后的时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在党的面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论对谁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管什么地点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他都用委屈和愤慨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装饰他的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“党内，分工明确"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批人整人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批人挨整……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着是一声长叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道我们的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是拼凑的宗派集团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活的黑白被如此颠倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的爱护"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说是残酷打击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他当成雪地冰天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有共同语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟要求党高高捧着他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一尊菩萨不能侵犯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他迷恋“国际声誉”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管灵魂多么龌龊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却想戴永恒的桂冠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的党在他眼中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过是皮鞋一双"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或古玩一件"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他，对野心家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却眉开眼笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么亲、那么甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他奔跑在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几个反党集团之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一架电话总机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这根线接上那根线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李又然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当右派进攻我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当阴云密布的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他眼里也充满快乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以为就要变天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党，他早就讨厌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然他还是一个党员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用挑选的字句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖着那颗恶瘤一样的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻想成为“大人物”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"效忠丁陈反党集团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他喊着：我要杀人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫不掩饰凶横的嘴脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这位资本的奴仆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟含情默默地回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在法国、在上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托派的头子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他带来的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"估计过于乐观了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反右派的大浪把他席卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他对着麦克风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面红耳赤，抖抖颤颤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们激怒的风暴中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年反动的老底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全被揭穿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她收集情报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她的反党阴谋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦心地献策，起草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她联络人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打电话装小姑娘的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知羞耻地叫“叔叔”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她订攻守同盟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在街头的矮树下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼鬼祟祟像个小特务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她的退却"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一个卖假药的商人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在党组会上说谎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为她——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的女皇和妻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背叛党，出卖党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}